query:
SELECT bd.id, bd.weeklyBonusId, e.name as employeeName, bd.weeklyRevenue, bd.bonusAmount, bd.bonusTier, bd.isEligible
FROM bonusDetails bd
LEFT JOIN employees e ON bd.employeeId = e.id
LEFT JOIN weeklyBonuses wb ON bd.weeklyBonusId = wb.id
WHERE wb.year = 2026 AND wb.month = 1 AND wb.weekNumber = 1
ORDER BY bd.weeklyRevenue DESC;
